ana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: #404040; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;hr style=&quot;color: #d4d4d4; height: 1px; border: 0px; clear: both; font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #d4d4d4;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Nested HTML Elements&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: #404040; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;HTML elements can be nested (elements can contain elements).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: #404040; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;All HTML documents consist of nested HTML elements.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: #404040; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This example contains 4 HTML elements:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;example&quot; style=&quot;width: auto; border: 1px solid #ebebeb; margin: 0px; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: verdana, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f1f1f1;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;example&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: normal; color: #444444; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;example_code notranslate htmlHigh&quot; style=&quot;width: auto; padding: 4px 4px 4px 7px; border-left-width: 4px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: #8ac007; font-family: Consolas, ''courier new''; border-radius: 4px; background-color: #ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highLT&quot; style=&quot;color: blue;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highELE&quot; style=&quot;color: #a52a2a;&quot;&gt;!DOCTYPE&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;highATT&quot; style=&quot;color: #dc143c;&quot;&gt;html